  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of Abaloparatide-SC in Men With Osteoporosis (ATOM)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Phase 3 Multicenter Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of Abaloparatide-SC for the Treatment of Men With Osteoporosis</official_title>
